ANC youths yesterday praised their leader Musalia Mudavadi as &ldquo;a great leader who has the interests of the youth at heart&rdquo;.Nairobi youth leader Esemele Amugune said Mudavadi will help the youth and people living with disabilities succeed if elected President.He spoke at a Nairobi hotel, where he was accompanied by youths from the 47 counties. &ldquo;He&rsquo;s the best person to address historical injustices and help the marginalised. Mudavadi&rsquo;s track record exemplifies transparency and accountability in his service to Kenyans,&rdquo; Esemele said.